info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actors.config_accessor

Class ConfigAccessActorBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actors.Actor
      • info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actors.config_accessor.ConfigAccessActorBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigAccessActorDb, ConfigAccessActorFs, ConfigAccessActorRam

    public abstract class ConfigAccessActorBase
extends Actor
    Base class for actors querying configuration. Every actor inherited from this class should have a getConfigSection handler which receives message with section field which contains the name of queried section, and responds on the message adding a field with name of section and containing an IObject representing contents of that section. If field is already non-null then the actor should not overwrite it.
